text: Iwanai District in Shiribeshi Subprefecture. is a district located in Shiribeshi Subprefecture, Hokkaidō, Japan. As of 2004, the district has an estimated population of 22,977 and a density of 61.17 persons per km². The total area is 375.60 km². ==Towns and villages== *Iwanai *Kyōwa Category:Districts in Hokkaido
title: Iwanai District, Hokkaido
